# source_id: 3118
# teaser: Evaluete and Audit existing content for SEO in order to understand if it answers the user
# intent AND learn how to improve it. by Joao Filipe Pereira
- id: 3118-content-analyzer
  title: Content Analyzer
  tags:
  - writing
  - content
  - analyzer
  family: writing
  body: 1. On a scale of 0 to 10, how relevant is this content for the query I'm trying
    to rank on google? And how can I improve it? 2. Also evaluate if I'm clearly demonstrating
    that I have expertise in the topic I'm writing about? And how can I improve authoritivesseness
    around this topic? All output shall be in [TARGETLANGUAGE] Below is the Query
    and the CONTENT [PROMPT]
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
